npm init -y initiate package
npm install --save-dev webpack webpack-cli
set up the scripts
scripts { start: webpack }
create the config file
PUT INSIDE THE SCRIPT "watch": "webpacj --watch"
ALSO "--config webpack.config.js"

const path = require("path");
module.exports = {
  entry: "./src/index.js",
  output: {
    filename: "main.js",
    path: path.resolve(__dirname, "dist"),
  },
};

put on the package json inside scripts --config webpack.config.js (inside start)

you can set the mode to development

to install SASS, go to webpack loaders page
 to install bootstrap - npm install --save-dev bootstrap
 do not forget of css and style loader

put watch option in the package.json

run npm start

